    "<h2>Send a message to begin a conversation!</h2>": "<h2>Send a message to begin a conversation!</h2>",
    "<h2>Welcome to Snekbooru!</h2><p>Please set up the essentials. You can change all of these and more in the main settings later.</p>": "<h2>欢迎来到Snekbooru！</h2><p>请设置基本项。您稍后可以在主设置中更改所有这些以及更多内容。</p>",
    "<h3>Guess the Missing Tag</h3>One tag has been hidden. Can you guess what it is?": "<h3>猜隐藏标签</h3>一个标签被隐藏了。你能猜出它是什么吗？",
